{\*\cs27\fs19\expnd0\expndtw-2\super{\super\chftn{\footnote\pard\plain \s23\f1\fs18\ltrpar\qj\fi-170\li170\ri0\sb0\sa0\facenter\sl200\slmult0\expnd0\expndtw0\cf0\up0\charscalex100\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\accnone\hyphpar1\lang1051
{\super\chftn}{\*\cs27\fs18\super }{\fs18 \tab }{\fs18 Podrobne SOBEK, T., KOT\'c1SEK, J., HAPLA, M. (eds.) }{\*\cs25\fs18\b0\i Pr\'e1\'76n\'ed argumentace. }
{\fs18 Praha : C. H. Beck, 2024. \par }}}}{\fs19\expnd0\expndtw-2  ktor\'e1 s\'ed\'63e nie je matematicky presn\'e1, ale pr\'e1\'76e dodr\'9eanie metodologicky korektn\'e9\'68o postupu je z\'e1\'6bladom presved\u269 ?
ivosti v\'fdsledku. Ani tu v\'9aak nejde len o\'a0scholastick\'e9 cvi\u269 ?enie. Nespr\'e1\'76ny metodologick\'fd postup pri aplik\'e1\'63ii pr\'e1\'76a s\'ed\'63e e\'9ate s\'e1\'6d osebe nemus\'ed vies\u357 ?
 k\'a0nespr\'e1\'76nemu z\'e1\'76eru v\'a0konkr\'e9\'74nej veci. Takmer ur\u269 ?ite v\'9aak sp\'f4\'73ob\'ed probl\'e9\'6dy v\'a0in\'fdch veciach. Tak je tomu aj v\'a0pr\'ed\'70ade ot\'e1\'7aky, \u269 ?
i je pr\'e1\'76nick\'e1 osoba bl\'ed\'7akou osobou, a\'a0kto m\'f4\'9ee by\u357 ? bl\'ed\'7akou osobou pr\'e1\'76nickej osoby. \par }
