 situ\'e1\'63ia, \'9ee cudzia ujma m\'e1 pre pr\'e1\'76nick\'fa osobu (ale nielen pre \u328 ?u) z\'a0majetkov\'e9\'68o h\u318 ?adiska rovnak\'fd \'fa\u269 ?
